		'seo_intro'         => 'Outdoor kitchen and BBQ area builders in Los Angeles. Counter, grill, fridge, sink, gas + electrical permits: a complete backyard entertaining hub coordinated with your pool deck.',
		'summary'           => 'Outdoor kitchens and BBQ areas built in Los Angeles. Counter, grill, fridge, sink, and run-of-show layout that works for actual entertaining alongside the pool.',
